snippet.title: Mists of Noyah - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist - https://store.steampowered.com/app/1168870/Mists_of_Noyah/?beta=0

Mists of Noyah is a 2D Co-op Survival RPG, in which you must collect resources to fortify your base, leveling up your skills during the day and fight the hordes of horrifying creatures that will hunt you at night.

https://twitter.com/mistsofnoyah
